@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Người dùng" as User #Yellow
boundary "ToursPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "ToursController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "TourService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Tour" as TEnt #Yellow
entity "TourType" as TTEnt #Yellow
entity "TourImage" as TIEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Mở trang danh sách tour
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Khởi tạo state filters\n(searchTerm, selectedLocation, priceRange)
UI -> API : 1.2: GET /api/Tours\n?Page=1&PageSize=50[&SearchTerm=...]
activate API
API -> Ctrl : 1.3: Chuyển tiếp request\n(không cần JWT - public endpoint)
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.4: Bind query params -> TourFilterRequest
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.5: GetAllAsync(filter)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.6: Tours.GetQueryable()\n.Include(t => t.TourType)\n.Include(t => t.Images)\n.AsQueryable()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.6.1: IQueryable<Tour>
deactivate DB

note right of Svc : Áp dụng filters theo điều kiện

alt 1.7: [TourTypeId.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.7.1: query.Where(t => t.TourTypeId == value)
else 1.8: [SearchTerm không rỗng]
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.1: query.Where(t => t.Name.Contains(term)\n|| t.Location.Contains(term))
else 1.9: [PriceMin.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.9.1: query.Where(t => (t.SalePrice ?? t.PriceAdult) >= min)
else 1.10: [PriceMax.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.10.1: query.Where(t => (t.SalePrice ?? t.PriceAdult) <= max)
else 1.11: [DurationDays.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.11.1: query.Where(t => t.DurationDays == value)
else 1.12: [IsActive.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.12.1: query.Where(t => t.IsActive == value)
else 1.13: [IsFeatured.HasValue]
Svc -> Svc : 1.13.1: query.Where(t => t.IsFeatured == value)
end

Svc -> DB : 1.14: query.CountAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.14.1: total (int)
deactivate DB

Svc -> DB : 1.15: query.OrderByDescending(t => t.CreatedAt)\n.Skip((page-1)*pageSize).Take(pageSize)\n.ToListAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.15.1: List<Tour> (có TourType + Images)
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : 1.16: _mapper.Map<List<TourResponse>>(items)
Svc -> Svc : 1.17: Tạo PagedResult<TourResponse>(data, total, page, pageSize)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.18: ApiResponse.Ok(PagedResult)
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.19: StatusCode(200,\nApiResponse<PagedResult<TourResponse>>)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.20: Response JSON
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.21: mapTour():\nchuyển ApiTour -> DisplayTour\n(gán rating giả, format duration, price)
UI --> User : 1.22: Hiển thị grid danh sách tour\n(có filter sidebar, phân trang)
deactivate UI

User -> UI : 2: Thay đổi filter
activate UI
UI -> UI : 2.1: Cập nhật state searchTerm/selectedLocation/priceRange
UI --> API : 2.2: useEffect tự động gọi lại\nGET /api/Tours với params mới
note right of UI : TanStack Query key thay đổi\ntheo [searchTerm, selectedLocation, priceRange]
deactivate UI

@enduml
